\begin_inset Formula $\nu\to0$
\end_inset

，得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
U(x,t)=\min_{y\in\mathbb{R}}\left(U(y,t=0)+\frac{(x-y)^{2}}{2t}\right)
\]

\end_inset

