\begin_inset Formula $\underline{L}$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{R}$
\end_inset

 均可逆，且有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\underline{A}\,\underline{R}=\underline{R}\,\underline{\varLambda}\implies\underline{R}^{-1}\,\underline{A}=\underline{\varLambda}\,\underline{R}^{-1}
\]

\end_inset

故 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{R}^{-1}$
\end_inset

 是一个有效的 
\begin_inset Formula $\underline{L}$
\end_inset

