\begin_inset Formula $\vert U\rangle$
\end_inset

 的方程 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:微分方程：双曲型：多波：线性"

\end_inset

 可以化为关于 
\begin_inset Formula $\vert V\rangle$
\end_inset

 的方程：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\frac{\partial}{\partial t}+\underline{A}\,\frac{\partial}{\partial x}\right)\vert U\rangle=\left(\underline{R}\,\underline{L}\,\frac{\partial}{\partial t}+\underline{R}\,\underline{\varLambda}\,\underline{L}\,\frac{\partial}{\partial x}\right)\vert U\rangle=\underline{R}\left(\frac{\partial}{\partial t}+\underline{\varLambda}\,\frac{\partial}{\partial x}\right)\underbrace{\underline{L}\,\vert U\rangle}_{\vert V\rangle}=\vert0\rangle
\]

\end_inset

即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\frac{\partial}{\partial t}+\underline{\varLambda}\,\frac{\partial}{\partial x}\right)\vert V\rangle=\vert0\rangle
